{"tid":678382,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人有睇想更認識你 (I Can Only Imagine)","createTime":"2018-05-26T04:42:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-26T13:59:11.000Z","uid":65400,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"971673a0ea5dc5f5b834afde510aad1606eea39b","tid":678382,"uid":65400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T04:42:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n感動神作 成個戲院啲人都係咁索鼻涕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a343cfb6cd4982d2d5fed96674c238c99b1a907b","tid":678382,"uid":65400,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T05:51:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"791049b79a214b8e41fda0c070e5692b9b81ce2a","tid":678382,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T07:24:09.000Z","msg":"本身麻麻地耶，但老豆死果場唱amazing grace都喊左"},{"pid":"2a1829942971d4923e3dd4b3b13e966aa4398da9","tid":678382,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T09:22:34.000Z","msg":"被譽為近代最受歡迎嘅福音歌曲《I Can Only Imagine》曾創下雙白金銷量佳績，原來背後故事都非常感人。最近歌曲背後嘅創作故事被拍成真人電影《想更認識你》（I Can Only Imagine），講述男主角創作歌曲背後原來經歷媽媽離開、被爸爸毒打等經歷，最後靠住基督教信仰先走出傷痛，創作出經典金曲，整個故事相當感人，低成本製作費下更「刀仔鋸大樹」，於美國上映時贏出同期大片《盜墓者羅拉》（Tomb Raider）及影后奧斯卡影后珍妮花羅倫絲主演嘅（Jennifer Lawrence）《紅雀特工》（Red Sparrow）。《盜墓者羅拉》及《紅雀特工》分別於美國本土獲5700萬（約港幣4億5千萬）及4700萬（約港幣3億7千萬）票房，而《想更認識你》卻有高達8300萬（約港幣6億5千萬）票房，認真唔簡單。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b8f6c5cbbdc42c3b5368501216ea86a406a8a16","tid":